data.description: 4169 Whitestone Road -- Built in 2012, this 4 bedroom/3.5 bath property located in desirable Sterling Green is ready for it's new owner! Over 3,000 sqft of living space throughout; just shy of 2,400 sqft on the main two levels, with an additional 700 sqft of finished space in the basement. 9-foot ceilings throughout.  Inviting curb appeal w/ a front porch and brick accents. The front foyer area is ideal for a sitting room, office space, additional dining, or a play area. Half bath is off of the foyer area leading into the open concept kitchen and living area, featuring a gas-fireplace. The kitchen makes hosting a breeze with ample cabinets, countertops, a pantry and an island. All-seasons room with so much natural light leading to the back patio & pond views. Full wrought iron fencing encloses the backyard. Upstairs boasts the 4 spacious bedrooms and 2 full baths including the primary en-suite with double closets. Conveniently located second floor laundry. The full basement is mostly finished with two separate living spaces and has a full bathroom! Plenty of space in the unfinished storage room with a newer tankless water heater. 2-car attached garage. Seller is offering a $5,000 carpet + paint credit/allowance. Brimfield Township. Field Local Schools. Tucked away in sought-after neighborhood with sidewalks yet close to restaurants, shopping, I-76, KSU, and NEOMED. Don't let this opportunity pass you by!
